        <div class="axil-privacy-policy">

          <h4 class="title">Shipping Policy</h4>
          <p>At Harisree Handlooms, we are committed to delivering your products in a timely and secure manner. Please review our shipping policy to understand how we process and dispatch your orders.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Order Processing</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>All orders are processed within <strong>1–3 business days</strong> after receiving payment confirmation.</li>
            <li>Orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed on the next working day.</li>
            <li>In case of any delay due to high order volume or unforeseen circumstances, we will notify you via email or phone.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Shipping Methods & Delivery Time</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>We partner with reliable courier services to ensure prompt and safe delivery.</li>
            <li><strong>Standard Delivery:</strong> 5–7 business days (within India).</li>
            <li><strong>Express Delivery:</strong> 2–4 business days (available at an additional cost).</li>
            <li><strong>International Shipping:</strong> Currently not available. Please contact us for special requests.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Shipping Charges</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Shipping charges are calculated at checkout based on your location and order weight/size.</li>
            <li>Free shipping may be available for orders above a specified value, as announced during promotions.</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="title">Order Tracking</h4>
          <p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number and link to track your shipment in real-time.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Incorrect or Incomplete Address</h4>
          <p>Please ensure that your shipping address is complete and accurate. Harisree Handlooms is not responsible for delays or non-delivery due to incorrect addresses provided by the customer.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Undelivered or Lost Packages</h4>
          <p>If your package is lost in transit or not delivered within the expected timeframe, please contact us. We will coordinate with the courier service to resolve the issue promptly.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Packaging</h4>
          <p>All orders are securely packed using eco-friendly and protective materials to ensure your handloom products reach you in perfect condition.</p>

          <h4 class="title">Contact Us</h4>
          <p>For any shipping-related inquiries, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:harisreehandlooms@gmail.com">harisreehandlooms@gmail.com</a>.</p>

        </div>
